    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Configure credentials\n- Microsoft Outlook node: Connect to the shared inbox with delegated permissions.\n- Airtable node: Point to the Buildings and Email_Log tables.\n- OpenAI (or Azure OpenAI) credentials for the LLM nodes.\n\n### Static data\nThe **Skip already seen** Function node stores seen internetMessageIds in workflow static data. Reset or prune if you redeploy.\n\n### Logging rule\nOnly log VIP, critical, or Instant-routed emails as per the `Prepare log payload` node. Adjust the expression if your VIP list changes.\n\n### Follow-up search\n`Fetch conversation` searches by `conversationId`. If you reply from a shared mailbox, confirm conversation IDs remain consistent across accounts.\n\n### Nightly job\nExtend the housekeeping branch to rebuild keyword lists from misroutes (for example, query Email_Log where Status='archived' and aggregate subjects).",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
